00:22:03.073 --> 00:22:05.075 position:50% align:center
Well, okay. Thank you!

00:22:05.158 --> 00:22:07.077 position:50% align:center
I swear, I'll protect it!

00:22:07.160 --> 00:22:08.953 position:50% align:center
[SAKURA]
We weren't together for long.

00:22:09.037 --> 00:22:11.498 position:50% align:center
But it was so great to
have you in Franchouchou.

00:22:11.581 --> 00:22:14.167 position:50% align:center
