because of a mix-up I caused.

00:22:25.387 --> 00:22:28.390 position:50% align:center
And it led me on
an incredible adventure.

00:22:28.473 --> 00:22:29.683 position:50% align:center
[KOTARO]
I see.

00:22:29.766 --> 00:22:31.518 position:50% align:center
Don't worry, I will keep
everything a secret,

00:22:31.601 --> 00:22:32.936 position:50% align:center
