00:22:33.019 --> 00:22:35.689 position:50% align:center
I mean, I wouldn't want to
lose my heroes, after all.

00:22:39.818 --> 00:22:41.569 position:50% align:center
Thanks for that.

00:22:43.947 --> 00:22:44.739 position:50% align:center
See ya around, Maimai!

00:22:44.823 --> 00:22:45.907 position:50% align:center
--Be careful!
--Bye!

00:22:45.990 --> 00:22:47.826 position:50% align:center
Franchouchou!

00:22:47.909 --> 00:22:50.912 position:50% align:center
Thank you for everything!

00:23:07.012 --> 00:23:09.973 position:50% align:center
[OKOBA] I keep coming
to the same conclusion.

00:23:10.056 --> 00:23:12.267 position:50% align:center
I can't find any information
on Number Five,

00:23:12.350 --> 00:23:14.352 position:50% align:center
