rest of Franchouchou...

00:23:14.436 --> 00:23:16.104 position:50% align:center
Saki Nikaido.

00:23:16.187 --> 00:23:17.772 position:50% align:center
Ai Mizuno.

00:23:17.856 --> 00:23:19.607 position:50% align:center
Junko Konno.

00:23:19.691 --> 00:23:21.693 position:50% align:center
Lily Hoshikawa.

00:23:21.776 --> 00:23:23.486 position:50% align:center
Tae Yamada.

00:23:23.570 --> 00:23:26.031 position:50% align:center
And Sakura Minamoto.

00:23:26.114 --> 00:23:28.033 position:50% align:center
No doubt about it.

